Description: Reads variant call files (VCFs) in a caller-agnostic way,
    annotates variants with flanking sequence context and transcriptional
    strand, and builds mutational-spectrum catalogs (SBS, DBS, indel) at
    several resolutions (SBS96/192/1536, DBS78/136/144, ID83/89/166/476)
    and in both counts and density representations. Successor to the
    numerical core of the 'ICAMS' package with plotting, Shiny, and PDF
    reporting removed; plotting is provided separately by 'mSigPlot'.
